Additionally, the rising trend towards holistic cancer care and multidisciplinary treatment approaches is reshaping market dynamics. Integrative oncology, which combines conventional cancer treatments with complementary and alternative therapies such as acupuncture, yoga, and nutritional supplements, is gaining traction as a comprehensive approach to cancer supportive care. Healthcare providers are recognizing the importance of addressing the physical, emotional, and psychosocial aspects of cancer care to enhance patient outcomes and improve quality of life.

